{"tid":1281191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我係藍絲]警方係71既行為真係好懦弱，竟然放班反中亂港既暴力人士入去搞破壞！","createTime":"2019-07-03T08:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T08:30:55.000Z","uid":251119,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd56560c3ec4939066aa919ab9941f81cb35edb2","tid":1281191,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:19:54.000Z","msg":"枉我之前仲咁撐警察，支持佢地用暴力打撚死班打壞後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到依家咁，真心覺得班廢警真係好垃圾<br />\n連班手無寸鐵，又瘦猛猛既學生哥都驚<br />\n我地交啲稅比你係廢架？<br />\n咁小事都做唔好，抵班學生反你地啦垃圾<br />\n之前支持你地就係想你地用武力維持番秩序<br />\n等香港唔再亂落去 好好保護香港市民既利益<br />\n但依家你地咁樣 根本就係蓄意縱容班黃絲<br />\n咁你地就係班黃絲既同犯！<br />\n立法會被破壞完全係警方既責任<br />\n要告既話就 就要告埋班警察辦事不力！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極度懷疑警方已被黃絲滲透<br />\n強烈要求徹查警方內部成員！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f824597b35ba7d81398e7d22e0ba9d6919da0663","tid":1281191,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5940e23e504d878bf455d09d1db69345f968b14","tid":1281191,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077af004ed2ea860639dae26eb2d69c5365df7cd","tid":1281191,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"push"}]}